{"tid":1741061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴警向香港仔中心住宅單位射催淚彈　警：為增安全距離減衝突","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:26:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f25ee1c3c449124108da67dd2e5ed10eb7f92288","tid":1741061,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一段影片顯示防暴警上周五（15日）晚上在香港仔中心，向住宅單位窗口施放催淚彈。《明報》記者日前向警方查詢，警方今（20日）回覆稱，警方使用催淚煙目的是為增加安全距離，減少直接衝突，從而可以有效驅散。 <br />\n<br />\n警方又指出，就彈藥使用有嚴謹指引，亦參考製造商提供的安全確認，確保所有使用的彈藥安全及操作正常。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191120/s00001/1574232672300/%e9%98%b2%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%90%91%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%bb%94%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83%e4%bd%8f%e5%ae%85%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e5%b0%84%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e5%bd%88-%e8%ad%a6-%e7%82%ba%e5%a2%9e%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e8%b7%9d%e9%9b%a2%e6%b8%9b%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191120%2Fs00001%2F1574232672300%2F%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%259a%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2590%2591%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25bb%2594%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583%25e4%25bd%258f%25e5%25ae%2585%25e5%2596%25ae%25e4%25bd%258d%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588-%25e8%25ad%25a6-%25e7%2582%25ba%25e5%25a2%259e%25e5%25ae%2589%25e5%2585%25a8%25e8%25b7%259d%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25b8%259b%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=aeda75c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191120%2Fs00001%2F1574232672300%2F%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%259a%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2590%2591%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25bb%2594%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583%25e4%25bd%258f%25e5%25ae%2585%25e5%2596%25ae%25e4%25bd%258d%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588-%25e8%25ad%25a6-%25e7%2582%25ba%25e5%